Convert BBCode syntax to HTML.

### Usage

In your page header, add a `type` property with a value set to `BBCode`:

~~~ .yaml
---
title: Page Title
description: Page description.
author: Taufik Nurrohman
type: BBCode
...

This is a [‌b‌]bold[‌/‌b‌] text.
~~~

